      "content": "i hear you, but it doesn't feel like a \"cycle\" to break. it just feels like the truth. i'm just waiting for the rest of me to catch up to the part that already died. it feels like there's no point in trying to fix something that isn't even there. why bother trying to repair an empty house?",
